<i>noun</i>: 하즈 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하즈</dt><br>
<dd>the fifth pillar of Islam is a pilgrimage to Mecca during the month of Dhu al-Hijja; at least once in a lifetime a Muslim is expected to make a religious journey to Mecca and the Kaaba</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: hajj, haj, hadj</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
